name: genhttplogs
readme:
# genhttplogs

**Node.js script that generates HTTP access logs**

## Installation
```
git clone https://github.com/mihailj/genhttplogs.git
cd genhttplogs
npm install
```

## Usage
```
npm start [speed] -s
npm start [speed] -s >> access.log
```
[speed] = optional parameter; float; ex: 20, 0.5, etc...; lower is slower
